  <h4 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-blue); letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;">DOMAIN: AI SYSTEM GOVERNANCE (ANNEX A.5)</h4>
