    <div class="control-item">
      <div class="control-ref">A.5.1</div>
      <div class="control-name">Intended Use &amp; Purpose</div>
      <div class="control-desc">Define intended purpose of each AI system in the cryptographic pipeline. PQC context: explicit statement that entropy validator is not intended to replace FIPS-certified TRNG hardware.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-item">
